snippet.title: Mothmen 1966 Teaser
snippet.description:
Coming 2022 to PC and Consoles
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1755030/Mothmen_1966/
Official Game Page: https://chorusworldwide.com/mothmen1966/
LCB Games on Twitter: https://twitter.com/lcbgamestudio

Mothmen 1966 is a 'Pixel Pulp'—a visual novel featuring a fusion of exceptional writing and stunning illustration, inspired by mid-20th century pulp fiction and 80s home computer graphics—set amongst the strange occurrences of the Leonid meteor shower of 1966.
